    public abstract class FullFunctionScreen
extends ClickableScreen
implements java.awt.event.KeyListener, FocusController, java.awt.event.MouseWheelListener
    The most common type of Screen, a FullFunctionScreen handles all types of inputs (typed, mouse, motion, etc)
